Privacy Policy for Ajik

(User App & Captain App)
Effective Date: 26-2-2026

At Ajik, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal data of our users and captains. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when using the Ajik applications.

1. Information We Collect
a. Personal Information

We collect basic personal information such as:

Name

Phone number

This information is required to create accounts and enable communication between users and captains.

b. Location Information

We collect location data to provide core app functionality:

User App:

We collect precise location data while the app is in use to allow users to request rides and determine pickup and drop-off locations.

Captain App:

We collect real-time location data while the app is in use and in the background to:

Match captains with ride requests

Track trips in progress

Ensure safety and service accuracy

Location data is collected only when necessary for service operation.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use collected data strictly for:

Providing ride-hailing services

Matching users with captains

Navigation and trip tracking

Communication between users and captains

Improving service quality and safety

We do not use your data for advertising or marketing purposes.

3. Data Sharing

We do not sell or share personal data with third parties.

Location and trip data are shared only between the user and the assigned captain for the purpose of completing a ride.

Data may be disclosed if required by law.

4. Data Security

We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data, including:

Secure servers

Encrypted communication

Restricted access controls

5. User Rights

You have the right to:

Access and update your personal information

Control location permissions through your device settings

Request account and data deletion by contacting support

6. Data Retention

We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to provide our services or comply with legal obligations.

7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any significant changes will be communicated through the app or other appropriate means.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:

📧 Email: support@ajik.com
